### Grunt Plugins &amp; Tutorials
It can be difficult to get a full understanding of Grunt at first. Here are a few plugins and tutorials to get you started

- ```npm install grunt-contrib``` &mdash; the master suite, everything you need to get started with Grunt
- ```npm install assemble``` &mdash; Assemble, static site generator
- ```npm install pretty``` &mdash; Code "prettifyer" for HTML
- ```npm install ```

### Gulp Plugins &amp; Tutorials
For your infomation: Gulp is an alternative to Grunt introduced recently. If you are not familiar with it or are unclear of of how it is different from Grunt, I reccomend reading the first two resources.

- [_Getting Started With Gulp_](http://markgoodyear.com/2014/01/getting-started-with-gulp) by Mark Goodyear
- [_Gulp: Streaming Build Systems_](http://slid.es/contra/gulp) by Eric Schoffstall 
- [Gulp Plugins](http://gratimax.github.io/search-gulp-plugins/)

